<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Your eSIM is Ready</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
  <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10b981 0%, #059669 100%); padding: 30px; text-align: center; border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0;">
    <h1 style="color: white; margin: 0;">Your eSIM is Ready!</h1>
  </div>
  
  <div style="background: #f9f9f9; padding: 30px; border-radius: 0 0 10px 10px; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;">
    <p>Hi {{user.name}},</p>
    
    <p>Great news! Your eSIM profile has been activated and is ready to use.</p>
    
    <div style="background: white; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0; border-left: 4px solid #10b981;">
      <h2 style="margin-top: 0; color: #10b981;">eSIM Details</h2>
      <p><strong>Plan:</strong> {{plan.name}}</p>
      <p><strong>ICCID:</strong> {{profile.iccid}}</p>
      <p><strong>Status:</strong> {{profile.esimStatus}}</p>
      {{#if profile.totalVolume}}
      <p><strong>Data:</strong> {{profile.totalVolume}}</p>
      {{/if}}
      {{#if profile.expiredTime}}
      <p><strong>Expires:</strong> {{profile.expiredTime}}</p>
      {{/if}}
    </div>
    
    {{#if profile.qrCodeUrl}}
    <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
      <p><strong>QR Code:</strong></p>
      <a href="{{profile.qrCodeUrl}}" style="display: inline-block; padding: 15px 30px; background: #1e90ff; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; margin: 10px 0;">Download QR Code</a>
    </div>
    {{/if}}
    
    <div style="background: #fff3cd; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;">
      <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Installation Instructions</h3>
      <ol style="margin: 10px 0; padding-left: 20px;">
        <li>Open Settings on your device</li>
        <li>Go to Cellular/Mobile Data â†’ Add Cellular Plan</li>
        <li>Scan the QR code with your device</li>
        <li>Follow the on-screen instructions to activate</li>
      </ol>
    </div>
    
    {{#if receiptDownloadUrl}}
    <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
      <a href="{{receiptDownloadUrl}}" style="display: inline-block; padding: 15px 30px; background: #1e90ff; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; margin: 10px 0;">Download Receipt</a>
    </div>
    {{/if}}
    
    <p>You can view and manage your eSIM anytime in <a href="{{appUrl}}/my-esims" style="color: #1e90ff;">My eSIMs</a>.</p>
    
    <p>Enjoy your travels!<br>The Voyage Team</p>
  </div>
  
  <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 20px; color: #999; font-size: 12px;">
    <p>This is an automated email. Please do not reply.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>

